data.title: Late Show with Stephen Colbert season 3 Joel McHale/Yara Shahidi/Joywave
data.meta_description: Stephen Colbert moves from his satirical late night show, "The Colbert Report" to take over David Letterman's seat at the long-running CBS late night talk show.
